{
  "stem": "12491.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as I said before, because we had contacts with people who had the right to make the assignments, we were given an-- an advantageous situation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we moved things like mattresses, sheets, pillowcases, some clothing-- as little-- as much as we could carry on that little wagon because we were allowed only one trip.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything else was left behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is so long back I wouldn't really be able to recall the thoughts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The thoughts were more about the future rather than the past.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have already learned by then that things of value have not-- no great meaning except as they serve you for the moment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You only need what you need now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't need what you will need a year from  now because you don't know what will happen a year from now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Therefore, all these things we left behind had little meaning to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we left most-- most-- all of our furniture, all of the stuff which you accumulate over many years in a-- in a family life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We took with us only what we needed-- what we knew we will need for next day, next week, or next month.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was fortunate to get an assignment to a Polish furrier who was given [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] fur skins from the Germans to-- to make fur coats for the wives of the German officers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during their furloughs, they used to take him home with them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for that purpose, I was-- I received a pass to be able to get out of the ghetto every morning and come back every evening without any supervision.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
